To build
$make

To launch chat application
$sudo ./chat

Receive 4KB data
$sudo ./receive_4k (note that receive_4k should be run before sned_4k)

Receive 2MB data
$sudo ./receive_2m (note that receive_2m should be run before send_2m)

Receive 1GB data
$sudo ./receive_1g (note that receive_1g should be run before send_1g)

Output
It writes received data on files (output_4k, output_2m, and output_1g)
